The paper deals with the task of script identification using deep learning techniques applied to handwritten data. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) domains. The use of multimodal data and deep networks also suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper involves experiments and evaluations of different methods, which suggests the involvement of information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
